{"tid":2459082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(假設題)如果立法要香港人打科興，大家會點","createTime":"2021-03-24T02:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T02:53:06.000Z","uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb0cfe1f89deafe252b0c6403aadebb65d282ee","tid":2459082,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T02:44:14.000Z","msg":"科興呢批預咗要香港人埋單﻿<br />\n就算啪曬所有藍屍到都好 <br />\n都一定有我地份<br />\n只係時間同方式嘅問題﻿<br />\n<br />\n今日看似可以&rdquo;選擇&rdquo;唔打科興就打其他﻿<br />\n但其實已經培養咗你需要打疫苗嘅心態﻿<br />\n聽日就可以立法迫你打科興先返到工﻿<br />\n大家就安然接受﻿<br />\n<br />\n又如當日安心出行大家&ldquo;選擇&rdquo;寫紙仔﻿<br />\n其實已經慢慢滲透緊啲意識要你跟住做<br />\n例如入鋪頭前&ldquo;習慣&rdquo;探熱 寫紙/嘟先入到﻿<br />\n<br />\n無錯大家都要生活﻿無奈跟住做<br />\n但只係希望大家時刻提醒自己<br />\n要知道自己個一個行為係做緊咩﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n﻿"},{"pid":"e84f76d35587b4c744b822737b969dfb186c5d54","tid":2459082,"uid":139187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"去親d鋪頭都係唔洗填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cb813e2387b278f19add27eba5008c02b17765","tid":2459082,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e84f76d35587b4c744b822737b969dfb186c5d54","tid":2459082,"uid":139187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"去親d鋪頭都係唔洗填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T02:49:17.000Z","msg":"仆街開錯吹水台<br />\n我明呀巴打，我都會係咁<br />\n但我地其實係小眾<br />\n而大眾已經好主動配合政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae87ebc4be9593fb60c888c2b08bc1a07c15f421","tid":2459082,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T02:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjCgyTZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjCgyTZ.jpg&h=aa566a96&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}